#

Crispy Skin Duck Breast with Cherry Port Sauce

30 min
$18.99
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreePaleo

Cuisine:

AmericanFrench

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

EasyGourmetQuickPoultry

Description

A succulent duck breast with a perfectly crispy skin, paired with a sweet and tangy cherry port sauce that elevates the dish to gourmet status, yet it's surprisingly easy to make!

Ingredients

  • duck breasts: 2
  • salt: 1 tsp
  • black pepper: 1/2 tsp
  • cherries (pitted and halved): 1 cup
  • port wine: 1/2 cup
  • chicken broth: 1/2 cup
  • butter: 2 tbsp
